\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Walter Sisulu University \'28WSU\'29 is a public higher education Institution registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and has programmes accredited by the CHE.\line \line The Institution is currently applying for accreditation of the Bachelor of Laws programme which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery at the Mthatha Campus.\line \line The Institution is currently accredited to offer the following programme\'3A\line - Master of Laws.\line \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
